node.text: Social media has changed my life. It’s been amazing but also made me realize that we need to show each other more empathy. Being bullied online is hurtful and also seeing my little sister go through it is hard. What do you do when you see bullying online? Many of us want to help each other but knowing what to do isn’t always easy. So when @UNICEF reached out to us to support #SaferInternetDay, I knew it was something I had to do. They've answered the ten most popular questions about online bullying. Tap on the link in my bio to get the answers. If you take one thing from our story, it’s that we’re all in this together. #endviolence
